name: Gordyville Media
overview:
Gordyville Media/Gordyville LLC has been operating websites since 2002, beginning with the inception of oddculture.com. The company is also active in search engine and social media optimization and website design and offers these services on a contract basis.

The newest addition to the Gordyville Media Empire is LOLFed, a humorous look at the financial turmoil of the times. It has been the subject of numerous stories and blogs such as the New York Times, Canadian Globe and Mail, the Financial Times, and Paul Krugman’s blog.

horrorfanzine.com is a new site dedicated to horror movie news and reviews.
